name: Artistic Expressions
description: A 3464 x 3464 jpg image created by taking my own design and unique algorithm along with my AI program to create the colorful visuals of emotion you see before you. This piece was inspired by the feeling I get when at times I realize I don't allow myself to see my full potential in life. There can be so much love and passion in my heart. However, I keep myself tied down by my negative emotions that hinder me from reaching my full potential in my work or in life period. This is a 1/1 piece. Any of my 1/1 art means there will never be any two alike.
